# 21. How to generate synthetic data quickly

You already have the strongest part done: structured domain documents.

Use your synthetic docs as:

- `data/raw/sis/*.json`
- `data/raw/mfg/*.json`

Each file should contain one document.

Example:

```json
{
  "title": "FERPA Compliance Guide",
  "topic": "ferpa_compliance",
  "doc_type": "policy",
  "source": "synthetic",
  "sensitivity": "restricted",
  "content": "FERPA protects the privacy of student education records..."
}
```

Do the same for manufacturing docs.

